Package: ddImpute
Type: Package
Title: Imputation in single cell RNA-seq data from correlations in both dimensions  
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kaiyi", "Zhu", email = "kaiyi.zhu@columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")), 
    person("Dimitris", "Anastassiou", email = "d.anastassiou@columbia.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Kaiyi Zhu <kaiyi.zhu@columbia.edu>
Description: An imputation method for correcting false zeros (known as dropouts) in single cell RNA sequencing (scRNA-seq) data. It features making use of the interrelationships between both genes and cells in the expression matrix, preventing excessive correction and predicting dropout values accurately.
Imports: 
    cafr, 
    jaccard, 
    purrr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
